Information.LongDescription: Cedarwood is a charming, 8-unit apartment building in a quiet neighborhood located across from Southwest Junior High School. The building has renovated three bedroom apartments. This area of Forest Lake is beautiful. Two other schools are within walking distance as well as many businesses including, Target, Walmart, and Applebee’s. Cedarwood’s apartments are warm and spacious. We welcome you to come tour an apartment. We are confident you will love calling Cedarwood home!
Information.LeaseLength: Month-To-Month, 3 Months, 6 Months, 9 Months, or 12 Months
